<p class="ql-align-center">据了解，车祸发生后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现场第二、四辆货车司机被困</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其余两车人员安全撤离</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于第四辆拉煤货车</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">采用柴油和天然气混合动力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为保证安全</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">消防员立即将第二车上被困司机救出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201102/abe8d30fbb0c400aae85e4cb45c366df.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/03bfce533846420584bc258aaaeb4a37.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在对现场进行可能泄露的天然气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进行稀释和掩护后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">确定现场无危险时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">消防员开始对第四辆货车进行破拆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201102/0279ca3f6d1340a3a80237f6d640d0af.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201102/39832857d89149e0b6138bb0f03517fd.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于车头严重变形</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经过40多分钟的营救</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功将第四辆车驾驶员救出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并且送上救护车</p>